data.description: Well maintained home inside and out.  Bonus space sunroom adds 205 sq.ft. (not counted in homes sq. ft.) for outdoor living with no bugs and AC comfort.  This open, light and airy 3 Bed 2 bath with 2 living areas is great option for those who just want to move-in and do no work.  All laminate and or tile flooring.  Kitchen has updated appliances, paint, tile and hardware.  Island kitchen with open floorplan to living and dining.  Suntube in kitchen dining area allows for solar lighting day and night without using electric.  Wood burning fireplace for added warmth should rolling electric during winter occur.  Primary bath has updated walk-in shower. Backyard completely fenced with newer stained wood privacy fence. Some windows have been replaced and have lifetime tranferable warranty.  Seller will need 5-7 day leaseback if possible.  Survey available.
